1)
wenquanyi_9pt.bdf
GPLv2+ w/ FE

bdfmerge.pl
PD

doc/*

http://wenq.org/
https://sourceforge.net/projects/wqy/files/wqy-bitmapfont/1.0.0-RC1/
from wqy-bitmapsong-bdf-1.0.0-RC1.tar.gz


2)
wenquanyi_cjk_basic_9pt.bdf
GPLv2+ w/ FE

is generated by the following command:
# ./bdfmerge.pl 0x4E00--0x9FCB wenquanyi_9pt.bdf > wenquanyi_cjk_basic_9pt.bdf


3)
gen_wqy_font_cpp.py

execute
# ./gen_wqy_font_cpp.py

update src/bitmapfont_wqy.cpp


4) change bitmapfont.h

extern BitmapFontGlyph const BITMAPFONT_WQY[20941];


======== Chinese ========
1)
wenquanyi_9pt.bdf
GPLv2+ w/ FE

bdfmerge.pl
公共域

http://wenq.org/
https://sourceforge.net/projects/wqy/files/wqy-bitmapfont/1.0.0-RC1/
从 wqy-bitmapsong-bdf-1.0.0-RC1.tar.gz 提取.


2)
wenquanyi_cjk_basic_9pt.bdf
GPLv2+ w/ FE

由下列命令生成.
# ./bdfmerge.pl 0x4E00--0x9FCB wenquanyi_9pt.bdf > wenquanyi_cjk_basic_9pt.bdf


3)
gen_wqy_font_cpp.py

执行
# ./gen_wqy_font_cpp.py

更新 src/bitmapfont_wqy.cpp


4) 修改 bitmapfont.h

extern BitmapFontGlyph const BITMAPFONT_WQY[20941];
